description:
In this video, we're doing a low key version of How Great Thou Art "Karaoke". This gospel karaoke is perfect for female singers who don't want to volume up the microphone too much.
If you're looking for an easy way to get into gospel music, this karaoke video is for you! This gospel karaoke is simple and low key, perfect for female singers who don't want to offend or overwhelming their audience. Come join us in singing How Great Thou Art in a low key, soft way!

Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters youtube production.
Karaoke Video made using Youtube Movie Maker.

Note: You can use this instrumental for your covers just include credits and link of this video into your description. enjoy!!!
